    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a pristine E46 M3, a masterclass in naturally aspirated performance. This example features the iconic S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering linear power through individual throttle bodies and an optimized double-VANOS system. The 6-speed Getrag manual transmission offers short, precise throws, paired with an M-Variable differential for exceptional lateral grip. Mechanically, this unit is flawless: the rear subframe has been proactively reinforced, rod bearings have been replaced with high-tolerance shells, and the cooling system has been refreshed. The suspension retains its factory-spec damping characteristics, ensuring the communicative steering and chassis balance remain uncompromised. This is a collector-grade specimen with zero deferred maintenance.",
